items.name: staged deepthroat concepts
items.description:
The premise here, is that I want a slider for how deep it goes. V3 almost does that.

Each of the individual stages, when used with their tags, can are deeper the higher the pressence. Ie. (stage five, fellatio, deepthroat, ballsdeep:1.6) is deeper than (stage five, fellatio, deepthroat, ballsdeep:1.1), I'm going to retrain again, and see if I can get a single keyword to work as that slider.

staged deepthroat and fellatio

triggers

  • stage zero: imminent fellatio

  • stage one: imminent fellatio

  • stage two: fellatio

  • stage three: fellatio

  • stage four: fellatio, deepthroat

  • stage five: fellatio, deepthroat, ballsdeep

  • stage6: after fellatio

trained on both the stage X words, and the tags; works better with the tags

if you want to turn them into gifs, like the sample, check out my animated gif helper scripts, grab the prompts_from_file_to_gif script.

This LORA originated from a distorted image and after self-iteration, the current fifth version of LORA is presentable.

The effect of LORA is to make a three-dimensional landscape appear on a girl's clothes.

Usage:

Trigger words: scenery_on_clothes. Then use scenery, 1girl.

You can make the girl's hands and feet appear by using arm, leg, feet, bare shoulders.

You can adjust the coverage intensity of scenery overlay by weight, usually between 0.5-0.9. I use anything4.5 and chilloutmix, but other models may work as well.

Please note the denoising of Hires. Fix. If you need more scenery, you can increase it, but it is not recommended to exceed 0.7, which may cause deformities. If you only want to maintain the current level and simply increase the resolution, the denoising is recommended to be less than 0.4.

You can change clothes. The clothes that have been tried are: dress, bikini, swimsuit.

Scenery with significant features that have been tried: forest, house, building, ruins, tower, Chinese town.

I believe this LORA still has untapped potential.

Feel free to try and upload images. This LORA will continue to iterate, and I hope it can have greater versatility in the future.

Why not give it a like or follow? You will receive notifications when it is updated :)

items.name: Change-A-Character: Bimbofy Your Waifu Today!
items.description:
Note: This is a Locon. Install the extension to get it to work. I've found them to do better when working on ideas that I want easily added to one of my LORA characters.

Another character changing Locon, this one specifically around taking your character and "bimbofying" them. It was trained on animefull_final with 63 images with the usual self-pruning and tagging. I like keeping my prompts simple for the first few pictures so that you can see it without a whole bunch of mumbo jumbo. Make your pictures better than mine though!

What does it do you ask? If you use this LORA without any other character LORA or descriptions, it'll create a someone with a thicc body, big breasts, and a relatively slutty outfit. I personally like combo'ing it with another LORA and at different variable to see different stages of transformation.

How to use it: The Locon strength best used is anywhere up to 1. Depends on how much effect you want it to have. Also the trigger word is:

BimboT - Only trigger word currently added.

Currently I have trained it to lean more towards bra/panty style outfits (though a usage of clothing trigger words should let it be swayed.) I've debated on making it lean slightly more towards skirts on a second version, so let me know what you think.

Extra, Extra!: Should be well trained and usable in most models. Images shown for example.

Picture Descriptions:

1-3: AnythingV3 using just this Locon.

4: AnythingV3 with my Shadow Sae Lora and this Locon.

5: AnythingV3 with my Sae Lora and this Locon.

6: AnythingV3 with my Hibana (Fire Force) Lora and this Locon.

7: AnythingV3 with my in progress Seraphina (Disgaea 5) Lora and this Locon.

8-9: AbyssOrange using just this Locon.

10: PerfectWorld using just this Locon.

What's next for this? Potentially a version that more balanced between the bra/panty combo and skirts when unprompted? Dunno if it's worth the effort though.

What's next that isn't this?

More character Loras. (Ghislaine from Mushoku Tensei, Conqueror Lilias from E7, Catherine from Catherine Full Body, Miku + Piscalat from Idaten Deities, Kuribayashi Shino from GATE, Rin Sohma from Fruits Basket, "Kasumi" from P5, Ann from P5, Ikumi Mito from Food Wars, Alice Nakiri from Food Wars, Chika Fujiwara from Kaguya-sama, Lulu from FF10, Momo from My Hero, Vivy from Vivy, Dominique de Sade from Vanitas, Dos from One Punch Man, and Seraphina from Disgaea 5.) And maybe Wilhelm van Astrea, my favorite Re:Zero husbando or a Prinny from Disgaea.

V2's of some of the previous Loras. Specifically make them more diversely acceptable with other models and LORA's.

I also have some more quite NSFW Locon's. Specifically, being pet play, being stepped on, brainwashing, corruptedv2, and one that might be too much for me to even upload here >.<.

And, uh, I want to make a few happy Locon's so I have an "angel-ify" your character one coming up. And a forest fairy one as well. And a soldier one. And a barbarian one.

Or just give me some random suggestion or priority opinions. That works too.

items.name: POV Missionary
items.description:
This is a LoRA to generate POV Missionary.

  • I suggest using this at 0.8-1.0 weight for best results but make sure to always play around with the weight.

  • It was generated and only tested using AOM2, AOM3 A1, My Own Mix, OrangeMix VAE and AnythingV3 VAE.

  • Always add this to the prompt to activate it: missionarypose, 1boy, penis, lying, missionary, vaginal

  • I suggest generating in 512x512 then upscaling to an higher resolution.

  • You can generate at 768 (height) x 512 (width) as well then upscale to higher resolution.

  • Unfortunately - It works best with the default tags. Variations work well but not as good as default.

You can small variations by adding these tags individually

  • cum, cum in pussy - adds different variations and adds cum (of course).

  • sex, m legs - adds different variations.

  • arms up - adds like one or two different variations.

  • motion lines - will add the effect of motion and add a few variations.

  • barefoot, feet, soles - will try to bring up her legs and show her feet but it doesn't work well.

Known Issues (As far as I know)

  • Sometimes extra hands will appear. She will try to lift her legs but her arms will be near her chest or somewhere between. This is probably because of the few pictures in the dataset or lack of tags to take it.

  • There are other variations but they destroy the generations, so I didn't add them. They might appear randomly though just because of the universal tag.

Robert John Downey Jr. (born April 4, 1965) is an American actor and producer. In 2008, Downey was named by Time magazine among the 100 most influential people in the world, and from 2013 to 2015, he was listed by Forbes as Hollywood's highest-paid actor.

Looking for something... spicy?Â Here's my Patreon! It will support my work. Also, I recentlyÂ started a blogÂ where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hey Civitai! What you see here is aÂ textual inversion of one of my favorite actors: Robert Downey Jr! I used 40 public images of him with an 8900 steps process. To use it in your works:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • addÂ robdowney65Â to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 20/30, and CFG between 7 and 7.5 to work well. Great results withÂ DPM++ SDE Karras & Edge Of Realism;

items.name: Based65
items.description:
THE PRUNED MODEL IS PROTO-MIX THE FULL MODEL IS FINAL-MIX

and basically with the image examples

LEFT is Proto-Mix

RIGHT is Final-Mix

CC License

I initially wanted to upload all the based-mixes onto one page but alas it doesn't work that way here, make sure you look at the huggingface repo I created to host ALL Based-mixes I have made so far along with all future entries that will be uploaded here too. Pruned versions with the model toolkit extension will be uploaded there as well for all previous Based-mixes and future Based mixes.

Based65 proto and finalmix were made with the aid of the Supermerger extension

https://github.com/hako-mikan/sd-webui-supermerger

Finalmix also included the usage of the MBW extension

65 was made with using HLL3's final epoch and AOM2_hard as the base, however despite me throwing some random mixes I liked to stray further away from AOM2's hard look (that realistic rib look that I didn't really like which also showed up on Based64) while maintaining its NSFW capabilities "Based65-Final-Mix" despite it's great appearance seems to have a harder time getting precise LORA details compared to protomix and Based64, the reason for this? It's due to the fact that apparently within the models I mixed some already included finetuned models that I wasn't aware of which CAN affect LORA compatibility so for example if your LORA details have trouble showing up on Based65-Final-mix the reason for that is due to more than 2 finetuned models were included in the mixing recipe, going above 2 seems to make LORA compatibility wonky, so my plan with the future Based mixes is to ensure that I take a close look at the creation process of the random models I put into my mixes and ensure that they're just another basic Anime model mix so I have an easier time ensuring that myself and users using my mix can easily generate "close to accurate" details with their baked LORAs.

So basically,

BE WARNED IF YOU PLAN ON USING 65-FINAL-MIX IN YOUR MERGES

Using proto-mix should be fine because I can only recall 2 "finetuned" models being used in the merge, I might just need to understand MBW a bit more to make LORA compatibility better with potential future Based-mixes using more models I'm unaware that are actually finetuned merges but for now I'll be keeping an eye out and putting more focus on the origins of the models I put within the mixing recipe for future models, which I didn't do for 64 and 65.

Yeah model merging takes time, well AI image stuff takes times once you decide to go beyond generating stuff so please support me on my socials or platforms where I post outputs from my models/LORAs or platforms where you can support me financially by donating/hiring me for services on the obvious platforms listed on this linktree, the money will be used to get bigger NVME SSDs that don't have garbage file caching so model merging doesn't have stupid moments where it's stuck and I have to reset the whole process.

items.name: Tamaki (Dead or alive: Venus's Vacation)
items.description:
Tamaki is a game character that comes from Dead or Alive Xtreme Venus Vacation. Itâ€™s my first character. It has been trained using chilloutmix . Because the dataset is 512x512 resolution, the character focuses on the upper body & face for now.

It will make it more likely to render in-game with high weight, while less weight would make it more realistic like. Most in the dataset is a bikini and resort, so "bare shoulders, cleavages, breasts, pool, beach, shore, sky" will be more often in high weight. I have tried to change the outfit and background, the result is pretty stable in weight in 0.7-0.8. so suit yourself.

You could call with prompt "tamaki\(doa\)", work with "tamaki face" and "tamaki upper body" to get what you want. sometimes the image will become strange so just try it several times go get what you want.

Please leave your comment here so I can see how to improve.

items.name: ã€Art Styleã€‘LAM Style
items.description:
2023/4/17 update

Assign different weights to each tag for training. Adjust linear dim to 64. The preview images of the new model are generated using 'Hires Fix' and upscaled with 'SD Upscale'.

Introduction

A Lycoris model trained with ~180 images by LAM. The trigger tag is â€˜lam-styleâ€™. The 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) are recommended. 0.6 ~ 0.8 weights are good. The preview images are generated using 1.6 version (original) YesMix.

Cautions (Must Read)

  • Some preview images are generated using hires fix. Thus, if you wanna generate the preview images, pls download the original preview images and analyze them using 'PNG INFO' in webui to get all generating information.

  • The maximum of generating resolution should not exceed 1024 theoretically, otherwise extra/deformed head/limbs will be waiting for you :). Try to use 'hires fix' to prevent this problem and help to generate higher-resolution images.

  • For 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) users, make sure add '--no-half-vae' in command line of webui to prevent generating black images. See voldy's log for the details of edit method. For high-performance GPU, make sure 'medvram' and 'lowvram' mode are disabled.

items.name: Persona Style Checkpoint
items.description:
-PERSONA-

This is basically a model that mimics Shigenori Soejima's art style.

To be precise, it was created by entering (Persona:1.2), (Shigenori Soejima:1.2) into NOVEL AI's model and aiming for a specific art style that comes out when you get lucky.

-Hard Update-

A hard model is one that pursues art style at the expense of most things except art style.

It's not a good model to use on its own, but sometimes it's what you need.

-Lite Update-

It's a model that aims to improve prompt recognition, backgrounds, light sources, and overall things like finger representation at the expense of some art style.

It's not a huge improvement, but hey, at least they tried, right?

items.name: Mermaids - LoHa
items.description:
Please check out my Ko-Fi page if you are interested in supporting me.

LoRA commissions open! -> Fiverr

This is a LoHa LoRA! You need the extension! Why? They do a lot better with multi-concepts.

Trigger words for V1.20:

positive: <lora:Mermaidv220:1>(mermaid, full body)

You can also try "monster girl", "pussy", "green scales" (or any other color WITH LIMITED results), "head fins"
LoHa is biased towards generating a "pussy" since the entire dataset had one! Use negative "pussy, nsfw" and "sfw" in positives for sfw gens!

Follow the steps in the Model Version notes to reproduce my images.

Sample images generated with Grapefruit.

All negative embeds should be easy to find. and Prompts should be included in the sample images! Click the little icon in the bottom right to see it.

It was trained on 75 512x512 images and 20 epochs using Animefull-final-pruned for the Training Model.

Danbooru tags generated by Waifu Diffusion 1.4 Tagger and manually fine tuned.

modelVersions.name: v2.15
modelVersions.description:
Generate using a weight of 0.5-1.0 like this: <lora:mermaidv215:0.75>.

Overall feels better with anatomy compared to first version, but still have problems with fins.

Dataset reduced down.


How I archived my generations:

  1. txt2img: DPM++ SDE Karras with 20 steps, 512x512(can go up to 768 for wide or tall), Restore faces on (using CodeFormer weight 1.0 in Settings), Hires-fix on, to 1024x1024 (double original size) with your preferred upscaler and Denoise 0.4, CFG 7. Then send to img2img!

  2. img2img: DPM++ SED Karras with 20 steps, Restore faces on (CodeFormer weight 1), rescale to 1536x1536, CFG 7, Denoise between 0.3-0.7 (based on how much you want to improve the image), SAME PROMPT! Send to extras when happy with img2img/inpaint results.

  3. extras: Scale to x3 (final will be 4608x4608, I suggest going lower, I did x3 just for the samples here) Upscaler 1 - FatalAnime 4x, Upscaler 2 - SwinIR 4x with 0.10 visibility, GFPGAN 0.10 visibility, CodeFormer 0.10 visibility.

If anyone is curious about my version names: v{version}.{trainingEpochs}

items.name: Female Bronze Statue
items.description:
Do you like bronze statues and would like to make explicit art with them? Then you are in luck.

Trained on 512x512 images.

Add words like bronze statue, made of bronze, naked, nude, and explicit body parts that you want(navel breasts, nipples, vulva, vagina, anus, asshole).

I would add words like dark skin in order to get a better color match for the bronze.

Bust is for closeup photos of the head and face.

hi-res fix is encouraged.

Clip-skip of 2

Strength of 1 seems to be too strong for some prompts, but play around with it and see what works best for you.

Models like Clarity seem to work better than Perfect Deliberate for full body images.

This is my first attempt at making a LORA, so any tips and feedback would be much appreciated.
